    __init__: Initializes the application and sets up the interface.
    build_interface: Builds the GUI elements (entry field, labels, and buttons).
    calculate: Converts the total time in seconds to hours, minutes, and seconds.
    update: Updates the time display based on user input.
    timer: Manages the countdown of the timer.
    start: Starts the timer.
    stop: Stops the timer.
    reset: Resets the timer to 00:00:00.
    quit: Closes the application.
    pause: Pauses the timer.
    resume: Resumes the timer.
